<subSubSection id="C317ABC4D9617A31FF2CFC76FDFBDDF6" pageId="16" pageNumber="539" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="8BB2F84FD9617A31FF2CFC76FDFBDDF6" blockId="16.[151,1437,836,1007]" pageId="16" pageNumber="539">
<emphasis id="B979245DD9617A31FF2CFC76FED9DDBE" bold="true" box="[199,322,908,935]" pageId="16" pageNumber="539">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Lower ocular lobe shorter than genae; metatibiae flattened and densely setose; scape pedunculateclavate; prothorax longer than wide; pronotum without tubercles; metatibiae flattened, entire surface densely setose. Number of species currently included: 2.
</paragraph>
